sources.title: 1935 Joseph Henabery Thru Traffic ( Paul Kelly, Marguerite Churchill)
sources.description: Martin Gray and Dan Holden are rival race-car drivers, and both crash in a big race and decide to give up racing and become partners in an auto-repair business. Cast Paul Kelly ... Martin Gray Marguerite Churchill ... Pat Corey Russell Hardie ... Dan Holden Leo Curley ... Logan, Crooked Politician Walter Fenner ... Hart, Crooked Politician Earl Mitchell ... Parts Salesman Directed by Joseph Henabery Story by Burnet Hershey Cinematography by Edwin B. DuPar, Ray Foster Film Editing by Bert Frank Art Direction by Frank Nemczy Details Country USA Release Date: June 21, 1935 Also Known As: Speed Devils Production Co: Melbert Productions -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- NOTATION: The You Tube Account " The Video Shop" has permission to re-distribute and commercialize any content from any of our sites
